                        A company can create a vocal service which welcome their clients with some Music On Holds,
                        customs messages. They can also manage calls forwarding or connect their own operators to our
                        server.
                        <br/>
                        This is a three month based project and it has been created by Pierre BOURGEOIS and Aur√©lien
                        SVEVI,
                        during an ERASMUS exchange between the University of Lille 1 (FRANCE) and the
